query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('security')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('certificates',
'encryption',
'hash',
'linux',
'network',
'passwords',
'windows');
